Description: (F)CGI executable for TinyOWS
 This package contains the tinyows CGI program.
 .
 TinyOWS is a (F)CGI-based framework for Internet map services which
 supports the Open Geospatial Consortium (OGC) WFS-T standard and
 PostGIS database backend.

